OL,6,FCameras will be allowed in Jersey
OL,7,Fcourtrooms for the first time.
OL,9,FThe landmark changes will see judges'
OL,10,Fsentencing remarks recorded for the
OL,11,F"most serious cases" and broadcast
OL,12,Flater on TV, radio and online.
OL,14,FThe Royal Court says it underlines
OL,15,Ftheir "commitment to open justice and
OL,16,Fgreater public understanding".
