OL,3,CCameras to be allowed in Jersey
OL,4,Ccourtrooms for the first time
OL,6,FThe process already exists in other
OL,7,Fparts of the British Isles - England
OL,8,Fand Wales made the law change in 2020,
OL,9,Fwhile filming has been permitted in
OL,10,FScottish courts since 1992.
OL,12,FHigh-profile examples in the UK
OL,13,Finclude Nottingham attacks triple
OL,14,Fkiller Valdo Calocane being sentenced
OL,15,Fto a high-security hospital order, and
OL,16,FSouthport murderer Axel Rudakubana -
OL,17,Fwho was jailed for a minimum of 52
OL,18,Fyears.
