OL,3,CCameras to be allowed in Jersey
OL,4,Ccourtrooms for the first time
OL,6,FIn Jersey, the changes mean the judge
OL,7,Fcan be recorded while delivering their
OL,8,Fsentencing remarks and, unlike UK
OL,9,FCrown Courts, it will not be streamed
OL,10,Flive.
OL,12,FInstead, one camera crew will film it,
OL,13,Fthen provide the material to all
OL,14,Fauthorised media organisations - once
OL,15,Fthe judge is happy for it to be
OL,16,Fpublicly released.
