OL,3,CCameras to be allowed in Jersey
OL,4,Ccourtrooms for the first time
OL,6,FThe media will be able to apply for
OL,7,Fsentencing to be recorded. However,
OL,8,Fthe court stresses that "broadcasting
OL,9,Fwill remain the exception, not the
OL,10,Frule" and "only where a judge, with
OL,11,Fthe agreement of the Bailiff,
OL,12,Fconsiders it appropriate".
OL,14,FThere will be no other change to
OL,15,Freporting restrictions and filming
OL,16,Fjurats, defendants, victims,
OL,17,Fwitnesses, lawyers and other staff in
OL,18,Fany Jersey court will continue to be
OL,19,Fbanned.
