OL,4,Ccourtrooms for the first time
OL,6,FJersey Bailiff Robert MacRae adds:
OL,7,F"Broadcasting judges' sentencing
OL,8,Fremarks is a way of increasing
OL,9,Ftransparency in the justice system.
OL,11,F"This is an important step in ensuring
OL,12,Fthat justice is as open as possible."
